Deploy the Application: Deploy the generated WAR file located in the target directory to your servlet container (e.g., Tomcat).

*Access the Application: Start your servlet container and navigate to:


*Run
Copy code
http://localhost:8080/investor-user-platform/
*Usage Instructions
1.Registering a User:

Go to the registration page (register.jsp).
Fill in the required fields and submit the form.
Logging In:

2.Navigate to the login page (login.jsp).
Enter your credentials to log in.
Managing Your Profile:

After logging in, access your profile on the profile.jsp page to view and update your details.
3.Investor Management:

Investors can register and manage their investment details on their designated pages.
Viewing Connection History:

4.Users can check their connection history on the connectionHistory.jsp page.
Database Setup
To set up the database, execute the following SQL commands:

*sql

Run
Copy code
CREATE DATABASE investor_user_db;

USE investor_user_db;

CREATE TABLE users (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100),
    profileDetails TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE investors (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
    password VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    investmentDetails TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE connections (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    userId INT,
    investorId INT,
    meetingLink VARCHAR(255),
    date DATETIME,
    FOREIGN KEY (userId) REFERENCES users(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (investorId) REFERENCES investors(id)
);
